00:01:31.716 --> 00:01:33.706 A:middle
should adopt to create great

00:01:33.956 --> 00:01:35.836 A:middle
voice and UI experiences for

00:01:35.836 --> 00:01:36.576 A:middle
your shortcuts.

00:01:37.336 --> 00:01:39.826 A:middle
And finally, we'll go over how

00:01:39.826 --> 00:01:41.826 A:middle
you can bring the experience of

00:01:41.826 --> 00:01:47.236 A:middle
