00:01:47.466 --> 00:01:49.986 A:middle
So, before we dive into all the

00:01:49.986 --> 00:01:52.186 A:middle
exciting details of adopting

00:01:52.186 --> 00:01:54.156 A:middle
shortcuts and custom responses,

00:01:54.936 --> 00:01:56.996 A:middle
